original: Dahlberg, Torsten Edvard, kyrkoherde, Kastlösa, f. 25/5/99 i Ljung, Gbgs o. Boh. 1., av Johan Edvard D. o. Ida Petersson. G. 33 m. Anna Ase-nius. Barn: Anna-Britta f. 34, Inga-Kerstin 35, Gudrun 37, Göran 38, Staffan 40, Håkan 44. — Stud:ex. i Lund 26, teol. fil. ex. där 27, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov siamt prästv. f. Växjö isitift 30. Vik. fiolkslkioli 22-23, fd. v. pastor i Vickleby o. Glömminge samt pa&t:adj. i Kastlö’s’a, vakanskyrkoh. i Kastlösa 34-38, därefter kyrkoh. där. Ordf. i ’skolstyr., kyrkostämma o. man-ta Iskomm.
translated: Dahlberg, Torsten Edvard, vicar, Kastlösa, b. 25/5/99 in Ljung, Gothenburg and Bohuslän, son of Johan Edvard D. and Ida Petersson. Married in 1933 to Anna Ase-nius. Children: Anna-Britta b. 1934, Inga-Kerstin b. 1935, Gudrun b. 1937, Göran b. 1938, Staffan b. 1940, Håkan b. 1944. He graduated from Lund with a degree in theology in 1926, and completed his theological studies and practical theological exam before his ordination in the Växjö diocese in 1930. He was a temporary teacher from 1922-1923, and a former assistant pastor in Vickleby and Glömminge, as well as a deputy vicar in Kastlösa before becoming the vicar there. He was chairman of the school board, church council, and township committee.
